# BMI Calculator

## Features

* Calculate Body Mass Index (BMI)
* Accepts weight and height as user input
* Displays BMI up to 2 decimal places
* Categorizes BMI as:

  * Underweight
  * Normal Weight
  * Overweight
  * Obese
* Real-time result display

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)

## How It Works

* The user enters their weight and height.

* JavaScript retrieves the input values and calculates BMI using the formula:

  BMI = Weight (kg) / Height² (m²)

* The calculated BMI is rounded to 2 decimal places.

* Based on the BMI value, the appropriate health category is determined.

* The BMI value and category are displayed dynamically on the page.
